There are 2 architectures based on which software configuration management tools works
1. pull-based architecture
2. push-based architecture

There are lot of software configuration management tools are provided by various different vendors in the market on both of these architectures
1. pull-based architecture
	- chef
	- ansible-tower
2. push-based architecture
	- Ansible
	- Puppet
	- Salt-Stack
